### AdGuard ###

### Some AdGuard settings I use in the Nordics.

### General settings

    Block domains using filters and hosts files -> ✅

    Filter update interval -> 1 hour (Feel free to change)

    Use AdGuard browsing security web service -> ❌

    Enable log -> ✅ (Not a bad idea to have some logs)

    Anonymize client IP -> ✅

    Query logs rotation -> 1 hour 

### Save.

    Enable statistics -> ✅

    Statistics retention -> 1 hour

### Save.

### DNS settings

### Upstream DNS servers

    https://dns.quad9.net/dns-query
    tls://dns.quad9.net

    Parallel requests -> ✅

    Fallback DNS servers -> Empty

    Bootstrap DNS servers ->
    9.9.9.9
    149.112.112.112
    2620:fe::fe
    2620:fe::9

### Test upstream --> Apply

    Rate limit -> 0

    Enable EDNS client subnet -> ❌

    Enable DNSSEC -> ✅

    Disable resolving of IPv6 addresses -> ❌

    Blocking mode -> Default

### Save.
